subtitleNullable: Captured Images of Cancererous and Non-Cancererous Lips and Tongue
descriptionNullable:
This is the image classification dataset of oral cancer.

It contains images of lips and tongue which are classified in cancerous and non-cancerous groups.

We captured images in various ENT hospitals of Ahmedabad and classified the images with the help of ENT doctors. 

You can try and practice on this dataset but We're not 100% sure about reliability.


Thank you!!
